  name: "Dirty Maneuvers"
  label: null
  type: null
  description: "At 2nd level, a cad becomes skilled at deceiving and discomfiting\
    \ his opponents. The cad gains a +1 bonus on disarm, dirty trick, and steal combat\
    \ maneuver checks. The cad also gains a +1 bonus to CMD when attacked with the\
    \ disarm, dirty trick, and steal combat maneuvers. These bonuses increase by 1\
    \ for every four levels after 2nd (to a maximum of +5 at 18th level).\nThis ability\
    \ replaces bravery."
  effects: null
